# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Keep Git metadata and project instructions.
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.nojekyll
!AGENTS.md

# ==============================================================
# CONFIGURE — choose one folder mode.
#
# Mode A: track whitelisted file types in all folders.
#   Keep `!*/` enabled and leave the folder list below commented out.
#
# Mode B: track whitelisted file types only in selected folders.
#   Comment out `!*/` and uncomment the folders you want Git to scan.
#
# For each selected folder, add two lines:
#
#   !FOLDER/
#   !FOLDER/**/
#
# This repo uses Mode A.
# ==============================================================

!*/
#!FOLDER/
#!FOLDER/**/

# ==============================================================
# DO NOT EDIT BELOW THIS LINE
# ==============================================================

# Keep text and source files only.
!**/*.py
!**/*.do
!**/*.ado
!**/*.m
!**/*.mod
!**/*.r
!**/*.R
!**/*.sh
!**/*.tex
!**/*.bib
!**/*.sty
!**/*.cls
!**/*.bst
!**/*.txt
!**/*.md
!**/*.json
!**/*.yaml
!**/*.yml
!**/*.html
